Unimart Store Data Analysis Project:
The goal of this project is to create a dashboard of annual sales data for a fictitious store called Unimart Store for the year 2022. This dashboard aims to provide a visually appealing and intuitive interface to easily interpret key metrics and get new insights about the business in order to make data-driven decisions for improving sales for 2023

Disclaimer : All datasets and reports do not represent any institution comapny or country and is just a dummy dataset to demonstrate Excel capabilities.
Tech Stack Used :Excel
  
Skills showcased in this Project
1.Data Cleaning, Data Transformation, Data Analysis
2.Filtering, Sorting and Conditional function.
3.Pivot Tables and Pivot Chart
4.Dashboard creation

Business Questions Explored:


